            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The asymmetry in the cross sections for  the  d(g,p)n",
                " reaction  with  80  to 600 MeV polarised photons has",
                " been measured  for  75  to  150  deg  s.c.i.  proton",
                " angles. Asymmetry sum(ang,en=eg) = (d(sigma(perp)) -",
                " d(sigma(col))/ (d(sigma(perp) + d(sigma(col))"
